title: The Impact of COVID-19 on Tech
itunes:title: The Impact of COVID-19 on Tech
description:
From factory shutdowns to canceled events, the novel coronavirus has wreaked havoc in the tech industry and beyond. In this episode, we explore some of the early consequences and consider what the long-term effects might be.
